        <abstract>
            <p>Sends ticket to pigeon show.</p> 
<p>A quotation from Erasmus Darwin’s <hi rend="italic">Zoonomia</hi> [1794, 1796] shows that he anticipated Lamarck.</p>  
<p>G. Grote impressed by <hi rend="italic">Times</hi> review [26 Dec 1859, p. 8].</p> 
        </abstract>
